
<div class="container-fluid upcoming_programs_background">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h1 class="text-center program-title"> Full-Time Web Developer Bootcamp, <%=@course.back_end_lang%> And <%= @course.back_end_framework%></h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
var images = ['upcoming0.jpg', 'upcoming1.jpg', 'upcoming2.jpg', 'upcoming3.jpg', 'upcoming4.jpg'];
$('.upcoming_programs_background').css({'background-image': 'url(/assets/upcoming/' + images[Math.floor(Math.random() * images.length)] + ')'});

</script>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row program-content padding-bottom-top">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h1>What You'll Learn</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <p class="parragraphs">The Web Developer Bootcamp is a six-month, full-time program. The curriculum teaches the skills and technologies required to become a full-stack software developer.
        For most of our students this course is also their introduction to programming.
        The core technologies that students use in this course are the three standard languages of the web: HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
        This course prepares students to work and build the front-end code associated with websites, web apps and hybrid mobile applications.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
      <ul>
        <li class="parragraphs">Program with <%=@course.back_end_lang%> and the <%= @course.back_end_framework%> framework</li>
        <li class="parragraphs">HTML, CSS and Javascript</li>
        <li class="parragraphs">Web application development and design</li>
        <li class="parragraphs">Application deployment and management</li>
        <li class="parragraphs">Skills necessary to join a development team as a junior developer</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid class-info ">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row padding-bottom-top">

          <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12 text-center">
            <div class="text-center fa fa-clock-o"aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <h3 class="text-center white">Schedule</h3>
            <p class="parragraphs white text-center">
              <% if @course.type_of_program == "Bootcamp (6 months)" %>
                Monday thru Friday 9AM - 4PM
              <% elsif @course.type_of_program == "Part-time Class (12 months)" %>
                Monday & Tuesday M/T: 6PM - 9:30PM
              <% else @course.type_of_program == "Professional Development (3 months)"%>
                Monday & Tuesday 6PM - 9PM
              <% end %>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12 text-center">
            <div class="text-center fa fa-map-marker"aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <h3 class="text-center white">Location</h3>
            <p class="parragraphs white text-center">
              500 Interstate Blvd S, Suite 300
              Nashville, TN 37210
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12 text-center">
            <div class="text-center fa fa-calendar"aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <h3 class="text-center white">Dates</h3>
            <p class="parragraphs white text-center">
              <%= @course.date %>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12 text-center">
            <div class="text-center fa fa-money"aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <h3 class="text-center white">Tuition</h3>
            <p class="parragraphs white text-center">
              <%= @course.tuition %>
            </p>
          </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

