          <%elsif @course.back_end_lang == "C#"%>
            <p>The second half of this course covers <a class="orange" href="../programs/csharp">backend development with <%= @course.back_end_lang%> and <%=@course.back_end_framework%></a>.</p>
          <%elsif @course.back_end_lang == "Javascript"%>
            <p>The second half of this course covers <a class="orange" href="../programs/mean">backend development with <%= @course.back_end_lang%> and <%=@course.back_end_framework%></a>.</p>
          <%elsif @course.back_end_lang == "Ruby"%>
